      "description": "We provide engineering, project management, and advisory services that enable the energy and industrial transition and strengthen resilience in society.",
      "text_excerpt": "Unlocking transitions | AFRY\nSkip to main content\nYour browser doesn't support video\nUnlocking transitions\nFind out more\nOur Offerings\nFind out more\nResilient solutions for reliable infrastructure\nBy combining data insights, environmental expertise and multidisciplinary engineering across the project lifecycle, we help keep Europe moving.\nFind out more\nElectricity grids are undergoing a transformation\nDemand is rising and power systems are under strain. They must be strengthened while still running. AFRY turns complexity into resilient, future-ready grids.\nFind out more\nLatest news\nAFRY partners with Endra for AI in Building Design\nAFRY wins IJGlobal Technical Adviser of the Year APAC for the fourth consecutive …\nAFRY analysis highlights how socio-environmental monitoring becomes key to attra …\nAFRY to design the Cavezzolo Viaduct in the Lugano Tram‑Train network\nInvitation to the presentation of AFRY’s Q1 report 2026\nAFRY and Holinger awarded contract for a new water treatment project in Berlin\nvisit newsroom\nOur offerings\nAFRY Architects\nAFRY Management Consulting\nAutomation & Manufacturing\nAutomotive & Mobility\nBuildings\nDefence\nDigital Solutions & ICT\nEnergy & Power\nEnvironmental and sustainable solutions\nFood & Life Science\nProcess Industries\nProduct Development\nProject Management & Implementation\nTransport Infrastructure\nWater\nJoin us\nWe believe that change happens when people with brave ideas come together.\nJoin us now!"
    },
    "about": {
      "url": "https://afry.com/about-us",
      "text": "About us | AFRY - engineering, design & advisory services\nSkip to main content\nAbout us\nUnlocking transitions\nAt AFRY, we unlock transitions towards a sustainable and resilient society. While others are talking about the future, we are making it. Through our deep-sector expertise, we help our clients where need for transformation is evident. Together, we turn challenges into opportunities and shape progress that lasts.\nWe provide engineering, project management, and advisory services that enable the energy and industrial transition and strengthen resilience in society. With 18,000 experts worldwide, we combine a global reach with local insights and deep sector knowledge to make a lasting impact for generations to come.\nUnlocking transitions is our promise to drive sustainable and resilient change. At AFRY, we don’t just imagine the future – we help make it. With deep sector expertise, we enable businesses, industries, and communities to overcome barriers and move towards a better state.\nTransitions require courage, fresh ideas, and new ways of thinking. That’s where we come in. We unlock opportunities that were once out of reach, helping clients grow, adapt, and succeed in a rapidly changing world.\nFrom securing essential resources for industrial advancements, to driving the transition to clean energy. From designing the places around us, to building the connections that bring us closer.\nTransforming challenges into action – we unlock transitions.\nQuick facts\nVision & Mission\nValues\nOur global divisions\nQuick facts\nArrow\n18,000\n18,000 employees globally\nAcross > 40 countries with AFRY offices\n27 BSEK\nNet sales of SEK 27 billion\n50 languages\nWe speak more than 50 languages\nWith projects across > 100 countries\n75%\n75% of sales in the Nordic Market\n75% of project sales\n75% of sales to private sector\nVision & Mission\nArrow\nOur Vision\nMaking Future\nOur Mission\nWe unlock transitions towards a sustainable and resilient society\nOur principles\nClient centric, Accountable, Empowering, Results driven\nValues\nArrow\nBrave\nWe think big and encourage entrepreneurship to increase value. Challenging each other and making bold decisions, always taking a stand for what we believe in.\nDevoted\nWe have a unique mix of competences and we are all passionate within our field. Sharing our expertise and insights to make a difference, we are driven by our curiosity to grow and learn more.\nTeam players\nWe share ideas and collaborate across borders to seize new opportunities. Challenging, supporting and bringing out the best in each other, we believe in the power of differences.\nOur global divisions\nArrow\nOur global divisions\nAFRY provides engineering, project management, and advisory services across three global divisions: Energy, Industry, and Transportation & Places.\nFind Our Offerings\nFind out more\nStrategy\nHistory\nTargets\nTrends and drivers\nPolicies & Management System\nSponsoring and brand collaborations\nFootnotes\n1. As of March 2025\n2. https://www.afry.com/en/investor-relations/financial-reports"
    },
